	uux.c (main), uucp.c (main): Call uucico with -C option.

	* tstuu.c (uprepare_test): Don't put the obsolete pty command into
	the port file.

	* spawn.c (ixsspawn): Set close-on-exec flag for both ends of
	new pipe.

