	* protf.c (ffsendcmd), prott.c (ftsendcmd): eliminate calls to
	alloca.

	* uucico.c (main), uuxqt.c (main), uux.c (main), uucp.c (main),
	uustat.c (main), uuchk.c (main), uuconv.c (main), uuname.c (main),
