	* xcmd.c (fremote_xcmd_init): Chris Lewis: use qdaemon->puuconf,
	since puuconf is not defined.

	* uuconf/syshdr.unx, uuconf/hinit.c (uuconf_hdb_init): Chris
	Lewis: added HDB_SEPARATOR to insert between oldconfiglib and
